{"tid":983293,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[勸世] 要預早計畫好升學途徑","createTime":"2019-01-15T23:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T03:16:11.000Z","uid":84472,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b960aacf8ad8dd6a8464aa36ba4856d62e1d4118","tid":983293,"uid":84472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T23:50:00.000Z","msg":"穩陣夠分入UGC嗰啲可以出番去先<br />\n<br />\n記得plan定好多個升學途徑<br />\nasso/hd/自資/retake/外國<br />\n<br />\n最理想梗係asso/HD入番UGC啦<br />\n仲有得同同期嘅人一齊畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知好多係讀完呢兩年之後係有offer<br />\n不過我都知有人得自資或者冇offer<br />\n<br />\n咁梗係可以攞住個gpa2.x搵工<br />\n不過你讀得asso唔係預咗讀埋大學先做野架咩？<br />\n<br />\nasso sem1唔過3可以話唔適應<br />\nsem2都唔過3你就真係可以打定輸數<br />\n你要讀嘅一早發咗力啦 sem3 4先出力邊有offer<br />\n負擔到 不如就quit咗佢去外國啦 <br />\nDSE唔係太低分都有學校收<br />\n總好過讀完兩年冇offer先再周圍搵<br />\nDSE完, yr1走, 讀完先走都係讀同一個course <br />\n點解唔嘥少啲時間 完DSE就走 <br />\n實有人話有錢一早讀過外國啦仲考DSE<br />\n個人認為中學一齊9fing個part唔skip得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重點其實係明知自己入唔番就唔係lur喺度啦<br />\n外國攞個Third hon都好過攞咗住個asso 2.x<br />\n讀過asso先過去唯一好處係人地year1啲野你9成讀過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5257dda9e5e0e352f6c5e09d51575ee81b311e1","tid":983293,"uid":70349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T03:15:39.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"4baae00eff3db765132876be70e83a42007534e9","tid":983293,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T03:16:11.000Z","msg":"55"}]}